* {{ill|Niutsuhime Shrine|en|Niutsuhime Shrine|qid=Q705154|lt=Niutsuhime Shrine|1=Niutsuhime Shrine}} (Kanpei-taisha, {{ill|Ichinomiya|en|Ichinomiya|qid=Q1656379|lt=Ichinomiya|1=Ichinomiya}} of {{ill|Kii Province|en|Kii Province|qid=Q864053|lt=Kii Province|1=Kii Province}})
* {{ill|Shirayama Hime Shrine|en|Shirayama Hime Shrine|qid=Q704702|lt=Hakusan Hime Shrine|1=Shirayama Hime Shrine}} (Kokuhei Chūsha, Ichinomiya of {{ill|Kaga Province|en|Kaga Province|qid=Q907469|lt=Kaga Province|1=Kaga Province}})
* {{ill|Anekura Hime Shrine|ja|姉倉比売神社|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Anekura Hime Shrine|1=Kureha-Anekurahime Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11447234}}
* {{ill|Tajihayahime Shrine|ja|多治速比売神社|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tajihayahime Shrine|1=Tajihayahime Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11430889}}
